elements.name: Standard user logs in, manages cart, and logs out

steps.name: the user navigates to the Sauce Demo login page
the user logs in with username "standard_user" and password "secret_sauce"
the user adds "Sauce Labs Backpack" product to the cart
the user adds "Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket" product to the cart
the cart should contain "Sauce Labs Backpack" product
the cart should contain "Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket" product
the user removes "Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket" product from the cart
the user resets the app state
the user should be redirected to the login page
